<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Phase 2: The OBI Magic on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/16-obi-ebpf/4-docker-obi-magic/</link><description>Recent content in Phase 2: The OBI Magic on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/16-obi-ebpf/4-docker-obi-magic/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>1. Add the OBI Service</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/16-obi-ebpf/4-docker-obi-magic/1-add-obi-service/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/16-obi-ebpf/4-docker-obi-magic/1-add-obi-service/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="add-obi-to-docker-composeyaml"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Add OBI to docker-compose.yaml&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#add-obi-to-docker-composeyaml" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="callout callout--success"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Exercise&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Open &lt;code&gt;docker-compose.yaml&lt;/code&gt; in your editor:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; ~/workshop/obi/02-obi-docker
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;docker-compose down
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;vim docker-compose.yaml &lt;span class="c1"&gt;#or editor of choice&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Scroll to the very bottom of the file you&amp;rsquo;ll see a comment block that says &lt;code&gt;PHASE 2&lt;/code&gt;. Paste the following block &lt;strong&gt;directly below that comment&lt;/strong&gt;, keeping the &lt;strong&gt;2-space indentation&lt;/strong&gt; so it lines up with the other services (like &lt;code&gt;frontend:&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;load-generator:&lt;/code&gt;, etc.):&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>2. Understand the OBI Config</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/16-obi-ebpf/4-docker-obi-magic/2-understand-config/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/16-obi-ebpf/4-docker-obi-magic/2-understand-config/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="the-obi-configuration-file"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;The OBI Configuration File&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#the-obi-configuration-file" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Open &lt;code&gt;obi-config.yaml&lt;/code&gt; (already in the repo) to understand how OBI discovers and instruments your services:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;cat ~/workshop/obi/02-obi-docker/obi-config.yaml&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;yaml&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;discovery&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;instrument&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;- &lt;span class="nt"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;frontend&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;open_ports&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;3000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;- &lt;span class="nt"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;order-processor&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;open_ports&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;8080&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;- &lt;span class="nt"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;payment-service&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;open_ports&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;8081&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;ebpf&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;context_propagation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;all&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;otel_traces_export&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;endpoint&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="l"&gt;http://localhost:4318&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="how-each-section-works"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;How Each Section Works&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#how-each-section-works" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code&gt;discovery.instrument&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; tells OBI how to find your services and what to name them. It matches processes by the ports they listen on, then assigns the &lt;code&gt;name&lt;/code&gt; as the &lt;code&gt;service.name&lt;/code&gt; attribute in the generated traces. Without this, OBI would use the executable path as the service name (e.g. &lt;code&gt;/usr/local/bin/order-processor&lt;/code&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>3. Verify Traces in Splunk</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/16-obi-ebpf/4-docker-obi-magic/3-verify-traces/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/ninja-workshops/instrumentation/16-obi-ebpf/4-docker-obi-magic/3-verify-traces/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="quick-verification"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Quick Verification&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#quick-verification" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First, confirm everything is healthy:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs" data-tabs&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs__list" role="tablist"&gt;&lt;button id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-en-ninja-workshops-instrumentation-16-obi-ebpf-4-docker-obi-magic-3-verify-traces-md-10-1--tab-0" class="tabs__btn is-active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-en-ninja-workshops-instrumentation-16-obi-ebpf-4-docker-obi-magic-3-verify-traces-md-10-1--panel-0" tabindex="0" data-tab-label="Script"&gt;Script&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-en-ninja-workshops-instrumentation-16-obi-ebpf-4-docker-obi-magic-3-verify-traces-md-10-1--tab-1" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-en-ninja-workshops-instrumentation-16-obi-ebpf-4-docker-obi-magic-3-verify-traces-md-10-1--panel-1" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Expected"&gt;Expected&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-en-ninja-workshops-instrumentation-16-obi-ebpf-4-docker-obi-magic-3-verify-traces-md-10-1--panel-0" class="tabs__panel is-active" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-en-ninja-workshops-instrumentation-16-obi-ebpf-4-docker-obi-magic-3-verify-traces-md-10-1--tab-0" data-tab-label="Script"&gt;&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;docker-compose ps
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;curl -s localhost:3000/create-order &lt;span class="p"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; jq
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;docker-compose logs obi &lt;span class="p"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; head -30&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-en-ninja-workshops-instrumentation-16-obi-ebpf-4-docker-obi-magic-3-verify-traces-md-10-1--panel-1" class="tabs__panel" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-en-ninja-workshops-instrumentation-16-obi-ebpf-4-docker-obi-magic-3-verify-traces-md-10-1--tab-1" hidden data-tab-label="Expected"&gt;&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;# docker-compose ps - all 6 containers running
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;# curl - returns JSON order confirmation
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;# obi logs - shows &amp;#34;instrumenting process&amp;#34; for each service&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the OBI logs, look for lines like:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>